data.description: Check out this new listing on Orchard Drive!  Brick 3 bedroom, 2 bath, multi level home with lots of space and wood floors. A nice size living room with natural light, dining room with walk out to large covered rear patio and eat in kitchen.  Step down to a spacious family, recreation room with fireplace.  Upstairs is 3 nice size bedrooms and a full bath.  Lower has a large laundry room and full bath.  2 car garage and storage room.  Close to town, mall and highway.  Home Warranty!
